[[File:Scalloped_hammerhead-tokyosealifepark-2019-1-8.webm|thumb]]
雙髻鯊[[物種|物種]]的體長範圍為 {{convert|0.9|to|6.0|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重範圍為 {{convert|3|to|580|kg|lb|abbr=on}}<ref>Hessing, S. (2000). [http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/accounts/Sphyrna_tiburo/ ''Sphyrna tiburo''] {{Wayback|url=http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/accounts/Sphyrna_tiburo/ |date=20120929055832 }}. Animal Diversity Web. Retrieved on 2012-12-19.</ref><ref name="record">{{cite news |authorlink= |title=Record Hammerhead Pregnant With 55 Pups |url=http://dsc.discovery.com/news/2006/07/24/hammerhead_ani.html?category=earth&guid=20060724100030 |work=Discovery News |publisher= |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=July 1, 2006 |accessdate=October 18, 2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622001318/http://dsc.discovery.com/news/2006/07/24/hammerhead_ani.html?category=earth&guid=20060724100030 |archivedate=2011-06-22 |df= }}</ref>。體色多半為帶有些許綠色的淺灰色，腹側為白色；深淺相反的體色可以減少雙髻鯊被獵物發現的機會<ref>[http://www.sharks-world.com/hammerhead_shark.html Hammerhead Shark] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sharks-world.com/hammerhead_shark.html |date=20110707050317 }}. Sharks-world.com. Retrieved on 2012-12-19.</ref>。頭的前部向兩側突出，形成外型類似雙髮髻的結構。在白天時常{{link-en|成群行動|Shoaling and schooling}}，在傍晚後則和其他的[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]一樣，為獨行的掠食者。

==分類與演化==
由於鯊魚本身缺乏硬骨，因此牠們鮮少能成為[[化石|化石]]，僅有牙齒較容易被發現。雙髻鯊似乎與[[第三紀|第三紀]]中期演化出來早的的[[真鯊屬|真鯊屬]]親緣相近。根據 DNA 分析研究，最早的雙髻鯊可能出現於[[中新世|中新世]]<ref>{{cite news| url= https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/05/100518113132.htm| title= Hammerhead shark study shows cascade of evolution affected size, head shape| date= May 19, 2010| website= ScienceDaily.com| publisher= [[University_of_Colorado_at_Boulder|University of Colorado at Boulder]]| access-date= November 9, 2016| archive-date= 2019-04-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190401175733/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/05/100518113132.htm| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

透過[[粒線體DNA|粒線體DNA]]的分析，得以建立以丁字雙髻鯊為[[基群|基群]]的[[系統發生樹|系統發生樹]]。由於丁字雙髻鯊具有所有雙髻鯊之中最大的頭翼，因此可以猜測早期雙髻鯊的頭翼可能也很巨大<ref name= Mutation>{{cite web| first= R. Aidan| last= Martin| title= Origin and Evolution of the 'Hammer'| website= elasmo-research.org| url= http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/topics/d_hh_origin.htm| accessdate= January 31, 2005| archive-date= 2018-12-27| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181227052545/http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/topics/d_hh_origin.htm| dead-url= no}}</ref>。另外，化石紀錄顯示雙髻鯊也可能在[[始新世|始新世]]就已出現<ref name=fw/>。

=== 頭翼 ===
一項理論認為雙髻鯊特殊的頭型有助於增加牠們的視野範圍<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1242/jeb.032615 |title=Enhanced visual fields in hammerhead sharks |journal= Journal of Experimental Biology|volume=212|issue=24|pages=4010–8|year=2009|last1=McComb|first1=D. M. |last2= Tricas| first2= T. C.| last3= Kajiura| first3= S. M. | pmid=19946079}}</ref>，位於頭翼兩端的眼睛上下側的視野可達 360°，這代表著牠們向上與向下的視野死角幾乎不存在<ref>{{cite news | first=D. Michelle | last=McComb | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/earth/hi/earth_news/newsid_8376000/8376740.stm | work=BBC News | title=Hammerhead shark mystery solved | date=2009-11-27 | accessdate=2010-05-04 | display-authors=etal | archive-date=2010-02-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100225034122/http://news.bbc.co.uk/earth/hi/earth_news/newsid_8376000/8376740.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = World's Deadliest: Hammerhead Sharks|url = http://video.nationalgeographic.com/video/worlds-deadliest/deadliest-hammerhead-shark|website = video.nationalgeographic.com|accessdate = 2015-05-23|archive-date = 2015-04-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150423144008/http://video.nationalgeographic.com/video/worlds-deadliest/deadliest-hammerhead-shark|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。頭翼也被認為可以幫助雙髻鯊尋找食物、提高獵食時的機動性、或是在急轉彎時提供穩定性。然而，牠們獨特的[[脊椎骨|脊椎骨]]結構就足以提供牠們轉彎的穩定性，並不需要頭翼的輔助。雙髻鯊和其他鯊魚一樣在頭部上都具有[[勞倫氏壺腹|勞倫氏壺腹]]，可以幫助牠們感應到獵物所發出的微弱[[電場|電場]]<ref>{{cite book|last1=Otfinoski|first1=Steven|title=Hammerheads and Other Sharks|url=https://archive.org/details/hammerheadsother0000otfi_y3q2|date=2000|publisher=World Book, Inc.|isbn=978-0716612100|pages=[https://archive.org/details/hammerheadsother0000otfi_y3q2/page/16 16]}}</ref>。勞倫氏壺腹也遍布於雙髻鯊的頭翼上，這代表著牠們可以感測的範圍更廣，更容易尋找到獵物<ref name= Hammer>{{cite web | first=R. Aidan | last=Martin | title=If I Had a Hammer | work=Rodale's Scuba Diving | date=August 1993 | url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/topics/d_functions_of_hammer.htm | accessdate=March 31, 2006 | archive-date=2019-02-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218042914/http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/topics/d_functions_of_hammer.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==繁殖==
雙髻鯊一年僅繁殖一次，雄鯊會透過咬住雌鯊來表達請求交配的意願<ref name="aquaticcommunity">[http://www.aquaticcommunity.com/sharkfish/hammerheadshark.php Hammerhead Shark] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aquaticcommunity.com/sharkfish/hammerheadshark.php |date=20190130105212 }}. Aquatic Community. Retrieved on 2012-12-19.</ref>，行體內[[受精|受精]]，雄鯊會透過[[鰭足|鰭足]]將[[精子|精子]]注入到雌鯊體內。為[[胎生|胎生]]，[[胚胎|胚胎]]一開始的營養來自[[卵黃囊|卵黃囊]]，而耗盡營養的卵黃囊將轉變為卵黃囊胎盤，類似於[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]的[[胎盤|胎盤]]，由雌鯊提供營養直到生產。幼鯊出生後，雌鯊和雄鯊都不會有養護行為，幼鯊會一同游到較溫暖的水域成長<ref name= aquaticcommunity />。一次生產約可產下 12 至 15 隻幼鯊（[[無溝雙髻鯊|無溝雙髻鯊]]則可產下 20 至 40 隻）。

2007年5月，科學家發現[[窄頭雙髻鯊|窄頭雙髻鯊]]可以透過[[單性生殖|單性生殖]]進行[[無性生殖|無性生殖]]，雌鯊可以透過將自身的[[卵細胞|卵細胞]]與[[極體|極體]]結合來形成[[受精卵|受精卵]]。窄頭雙髻鯊為最早發現有這項行為的鯊魚<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chapman |first1=DD |last2=Shivji |first2=MS |last3=Louis |first3=E |last4=Sommer |first4=J |last5=Fletcher |first5=H |last6=Prodöhl |first6=PA |title=Virgin birth in a hammerhead shark |volume=3 |issue=4 |date=2007-08-22 |journal=[[Biology_Letters|Biology Letters]]  |doi=10.1098/rsbl.2007.0189 |pmc=2390672 |pmid=17519185 |pages=425–7}}</ref>。

==食性==
雙髻鯊的食性十分多樣，包括[[魚類|魚類]]、[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]、[[魷魚|魷魚]]、[[章魚|章魚]]、與[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]，尤其喜好[[魟魚|魟魚]]。雙髻鯊多半發現於[[海床|海床]]上尋找獵物，牠們獨特的頭翼可以當作獵捕獵物時的武器，可以用來壓住魟魚<ref name= aquaticcommunity />。無溝雙髻鯊的攻擊性較其他雙髻鯊強，甚至有[[同類相食|同類相食]]的行為，對象包括自己的後代<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.enchantedlearning.com/subjects/sharks/species/Hammerhead.shtml| title= Great hammerhead shark| publisher= Enchanted Learning Software| website= EnchantedLearning.com| access-date= December 19, 2012| archive-date= 2018-12-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181230230713/https://www.enchantedlearning.com/subjects/sharks/species/Hammerhead.shtml| dead-url= no}}</ref>。除了動物之外，窄頭雙髻鯊也會以[[海草|海草]]為食，甚至比例高於肉類，並且有能力消化這些海草。牠們可能是目前唯一已知的[[雜食性|雜食性]]鯊魚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2017/06/bonnethead-sharks-eat-seagrass/|title=This Shark Eats Grass, and No One Knows Why|date=29 June 2017|author=Hannah Lang|website=National Geographic|accessdate=2019-02-13|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423105833/https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2017/06/bonnethead-sharks-eat-seagrass/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

